page.title: 07FOOD
page.content: There are many different kinds of food in Gt. Britain.Here are some of them,starting with chips.Chips are potoatoes cut in to little sections. Fish are sea creatures that live in water,they are caught by fishermen and taken to a factory where they are preoared for the public.Fish is sometimes severd with chips. Sausages are made from, the meat from the pig they are sometimes severed with potoatoes which are mashed up. Sweetcorn is a vegetable which is eaten with butter . Sheperds pie is compiled of potoatoes and mince meat which is from the meat of a bullock
